name: Lip Sync Battle
overview: Each episode features two A-list celebrities like you've never seen them before - syncing their hearts out in hysterically epic performances. Hosted by LL Cool J with colorful commentary by social media maven and supermodel co-host, Chrissy Teigen. The mic is off, the battle is on!

episodes.name: Jimmy Fallon vs. Dwayne Johnson
episodes.overview: The host of The Tonight Show Jimmy Fallon gets in the ring with professional actor, producer and wrestler Dwayne Johnson.

episodes.name: John Legend vs. Common
episodes.overview: Each took home an Oscar, but who will snag coveted honor of the Lip Sync Battle Champion? Soul singer John Legend and hip hop star Common go from collaborators to competitors in this epic battle.

episodes.name: Anne Hathaway vs. Emily Blunt
episodes.overview: They faced off in The Devil Wears Prada and now they're back for a lip sync battle royale. This week on Lip Sync Battle: Emily Blunt and Anne Hathaway!

episodes.name: Anna Kendrick vs. John Krasinski
episodes.overview: She may be pitch perfect, but can Anna Kendrick beat the King of Lip Sync, John Kransinski?

episodes.overview: Iron Mike Tyson takes on former American football player and actor Terry Crews in battle. But brawn won't help them in this match. It's a Lip Sync Battle War of the Roses!
